@startuml optic_batching_rounds

!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ncosta-ic/catppuccin-macchiato-plantuml-theme/main/theme.puml

title Applicative collapses, flatMap doesn't

participant "Program" as P
participant "Runner" as R
participant "Backend" as B

== Pure applicative (N foci, 1 round) ==
P -> R : ap(ap(f, fetch a),\n     fetch b), fetch c)
R -> B : { a, b, c }
B --> R : { a:..., b:..., c:... }
R --> P : value

== flatMap dependency chain (3 rounds) ==
P -> R : fetch(a).flatMap(\n   x -> fetch(x.next))
R -> B : { a }
B --> R : { a:... }
note right of R
  Now we know what to ask for next.
end note
R -> B : { a.next }
B --> R : { a.next:... }
R -> B : { a.next.next }
B --> R : { ... }
R --> P : value

@enduml
